  <p style="margin-top:0.3rem; font-size:0.72rem;">Research sources: Cuddy (2012, 2018) ¬∑ Kahneman (2011) ¬∑ Zak (2013) ¬∑ Willis & Todorov (2006) ¬∑ Ebbinghaus ¬∑ Rivera (2012) ¬∑ Walker (2017) ¬∑ Ratey (2008)</p>
